viewData.name: ASUS 14" VivoBook F441BA Laptop
viewData.short_description: Buy ASUS 14" VivoBook F441BA Laptop featuring 3.1 GHz AMD A9-9425 Dual-Core, 8GB DDR4 | 256GB SATA SSD 14" 1920 x 1080 Full HD Display. Review ASUS
viewData.long_description: The 14" VivoBook F441BA Laptop from Asus is designed for daily computing needs such as browsing the internet, composing and editing documents, watching videos, and more. Specs-wise, it's equipped with a 3.1 GHz AMD A9-9425 dual-core processor, 8GB of DDR4 RAM, and a 256GB SATA SSD. Its 14" display, driven by integrated AMD Radeon R5 graphics, features a 1920 x 1080 resolution for crisp and clear Full HD content playback. Other integrated features include a multi-format card reader, 802.11n Wi-Fi, Bluetooth 4.0, USB Type-A and Type-C ports, VGA and HDMI outputs, a webcam, microphone, speakers, and a 3.5 mm combo audio jack. The operating system installed is Windows 10 (64-Bit).
